    "patch_code": "protected List<Node> cloneChildren() {\n  ArrayList<Node> children = new ArrayList<>();\n  Node c = firstChild;\n  while (c != null) {\n    children.add(c);\n    c = c.nextSibling;\n  }\n  return children;\n}",
